CBRE are pleased to offer 75 Mica Street to the market. This is a rare opportunity to secure Larapinta's newest industrial facility setting new benchmarks for design and functionality in the Brisbane market.

Features of the property include:
- 2,500sqm Functional drive through warehouse
- 2 x 5 tonne overhead gantry cranes
- Large 3 phase power supply (transformer onsite)
- 240sqm Corporate freestanding office
- 12,000sqm industrial site with significant street frontage
- Excellent car parking onsite with separated access for passenger vehicles
- Over 8,000sqm of floodlit concrete hardstand
- 2 Access driveways giving superb truck access
- General Industry zoning (24/7 use)

This functional facility benefits from direct access to the Ipswich and Logan Motorways. Carole Park is a highly sought after Industrial precinct located in the Western Corridor.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE the Exclusive Agents.

Features of this prime facility include:

- 384sqm Corporate offices over 2 floors
- 1,856sqm Clearspan warehouse
- ESFR sprinkler systems throughout
- 9m+ internal warehouse height
- 3 Phase power supply
- Provisions for gantry cranes
- Amenities and lunch rooms
- 4 x container height roller door access
- External storage at the rear of the building
- Two large driveways from Silica Street
- Ample onsite carparks
- Fully secure site

Located in the highly sought after Western Corridor, Carole Park is situated only 19 radial kilometres from the CBD. The site offers direct access to the Logan Motorway and proximity to other major arterials including the Ipswich and Centenary Motorways.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE the joint exclusive marketing agents.
